9:52 Write a shell script to print numbers divided by 3 & 5 and not 15
Answer:
#!/bin/bash

for i in {1..100}
do
if ([ $(expr $i % 3) -eq 0 ] || [ $(expr $i % 5) -eq 0 ]) && [ $(expr $i % 15) -ne 0 ]
then
        echo "$i"
fi
done
